  <head>
    <title>Other support</title>
    <abstract>
      <para>Other ways of supporting the SDG</para>
    </abstract>
  </head>
  
  <formalpara><title>Sponsorships</title><para> Sponsoring
      opportunities are open to any company, organization, or
      individual seeking to be recognized for supporting the
      <acronym>SDG</acronym>.  Sponsors will receive recognition on
      the <acronym>SDG</acronym> web-site and through other
      <acronym>SDG</acronym> communications and events depending of
      the level of sponsorship.</para></formalpara>
  
  <formalpara><title>In-kind donations</title><para> Groups and
      individuals contributing code to the core Swarm package,
      contributing text to the Swarm documentation, supplying
      equipment, and/or contributing to the running of the Swarm
      Development Group are eligible for discounted membership
      prices.</para></formalpara>

  <formalpara>
    <title>Gifts, grants and contributions</title> <para>Gifts, grants
    and other contributions will be greatly appreciated.</para>
  </formalpara>
  
